PS C:\WINDOWS\system32> New-SelfSignedCertificate -DnsName "NAYOUNGKIM" -CertStoreLocation "Cert:\LocalMachine\My"
>>
   PSParentPath: Microsoft.PowerShell.Security\Certificate::LocalMachine\My
Thumbprint                                Subject
